<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Saldo Card – Support & Account Deletion</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Saldo Card support information and account deletion instructions." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1220;
      --bg-soft: #111a2b;
      --card: rgba(17, 26, 43, 0.78);
      --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --text: #eef4ff;
      --muted: #aab7cf;
      --accent: #4f8cff;
      --accent-2: #7a5cff;
      --success: #1fbf75;
      --danger: #ff5d73;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      --radius: 24px;
      --radius-sm: 16px;
      --max: 1100px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.24), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(122, 92, 255, 0.18), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #09101c 0%, #0b1220 45%, #0d1524 100%);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 32px;
    }

    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.15), rgba(122, 92, 255, 0.12)), var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -60px -60px auto;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.35), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      color: #d8e4ff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.8rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform .18s ease, opacity .18s ease, background .18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.96;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.28);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 18px 0 24px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .grid-2 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .card h2, .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .feature {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .icon {
      flex: 0 0 44px;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.18), rgba(122, 92, 255, 0.18));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .contact-list, .steps, .notes {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .contact-list li,
    .steps li,
    .notes li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-box {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    }

    .contact-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .02em;
    }

    .tag-ok {
      background: rgba(31, 191, 117, 0.14);
      color: #97f1c1;
      border: 1px solid rgba(31, 191, 117, 0.24);
    }

    .tag-danger {
      background: rgba(255, 93, 115, 0.12);
      color: #ffb3bf;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 93, 115, 0.22);
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 18px 0 56px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid-3,
      .grid-2 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 36px;
      }

      .hero-card {
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .contact-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Saldo Card • dev.of.beirut.com • 12-06-2026</div>
        <h1>Support, account deletion, and app information</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Saldo Card is designed for phone store owners to showcase available devices for sale,
          offer recharge keys for Lebanese and other phone lines, and simplify purchases using an
          in-app balance that cannot be used outside the application.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#delete-account">Delete Account</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#support">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container grid grid-3">
        <article class="card feature">
          <div class="icon">📱</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Device showcase</h3>
            <p class="muted">Display available devices for sale in a clear and organized way for store owners and customers.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card feature">
          <div class="icon">⚡</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Recharge key sales</h3>
            <p class="muted">Sell keys for Lebanese and other phone lines through a simple and efficient in-app workflow.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card feature">
          <div class="icon">💳</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Internal balance only</h3>
            <p class="muted">The in-app balance is used only inside Saldo Card and cannot be transferred or used outside the app.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="support" class="section">
      <div class="container grid grid-2">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Customer support</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            You can contact Saldo Card support at any time if you encounter any issue while using the app.
            You can also press the <strong>Support</strong> button on the <strong>Store Code</strong> page and choose to communicate by email or phone.
          </p>

          <div class="contact-box">
            <div class="contact-item">
              <div>
                <strong>Email</strong>
                <span class="muted">malltech.support.leb@hotmail.com</span>
              </div>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="mailto:malltech.support.leb@hotmail.com">Send Email</a>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-item">
              <div>
                <strong>Phone</strong>
                <span class="muted">+96179316053</span>
              </div>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="tel:+96179316053">Call Support</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>Important information</h2>
          <ul class="notes">
            <li>The most common issue is losing internet connection while using the app.</li>
            <li>Saldo Card does not function without an internet connection.</li>
            <li>Users cannot interact with the app until the internet connection is restored.</li>
            <li>Please do not hesitate to contact support if you need assistance.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="delete-account" class="section">
      <div class="container grid grid-2">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>How to delete an account</h2>

          <h3>1. From the Home Page</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>Open the drawer by pressing the menu icon.</li>
            <li>Locate and select the <strong>Delete Account</strong> button, highlighted in red.</li>
          </ol>

          <h3>2. From the Store Page</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>Press the settings icon.</li>
            <li>Locate and select the <strong>Delete Account</strong> button, highlighted in red.</li>
          </ol>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>Confirmation and data removal</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            When you press the <strong>Delete Account</strong> button, a confirmation prompt will appear.
            If you want to permanently delete your account, press <strong>Yes</strong> to confirm.
          </p>

          <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin: 14px 0 18px;">
            <span class="tag tag-danger">Permanent action</span>
            <span class="tag tag-ok">Manual confirmation required</span>
          </div>

          <ul class="notes">
            <li>Deleting your account permanently removes all your data from our database.</li>
            <li>This action is irreversible.</li>
            <li>Once your data is deleted, it cannot be recovered.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© Saldo Card • dev.of.beirut.com • 12-06-2026</p>
      <p class="small">Modern support and account deletion page for Saldo Card.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
